<p> The benefits of healthy soil includes:
<ol>
<li>Soil sustains life.</li>
<li>Soil contains many nutrients needed by all plants to grow. </li>
<li>Healthy soil aids in the cleanliness of the environment -decreasing erosion and air pollution.</li>

